Program: Discovery
Title: In Einstein's shadow - general relativity
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jryxy
Last Broadcast Date: 05 April 2005
A series of programmes on the work of Albert Einstein. How all cosmology today is essentially based on Einstein's theory of general relativity and so far, every prediction he made about the universe has turned out to be true. The programme is presented by Dr Brian Cox.